info.name: Chicken Basmati Biryani
info.description: Basmati Chicken Biryani is a classic and aromatic Indian rice dish made with long-grain basmati rice and marinated chicken cooked together with a blend of fragrant spices.

info.name: Suspense Chicken Fried Rice
info.description: Chicken Suspense Fried Rice is a bold and flavorful Indo-Chinese fusion dish with a spicy twist and a surprise element in every bite.

info.name: Chicken Fried Rice
info.description: Chicken Fried Rice is a savory and satisfying dish featuring tender chunks of chicken mixed with stir-fried rice and a variety of vegetables. The chicken is cooked until golden and tender, then combined with aromatic garlic and onions. The rice is tossed with soy sauce and, optionally, oyster sauce for a rich umami flavor. The dish often includes colorful vegetables like bell peppers, carrots, and peas, adding both texture and nutrition

info.name: Schezwan Chicken Fried Rice
info.description: Schezwan Chicken Fried Rice is a delicious Indo-Chinese dish that combines tender chicken pieces with spicy Schezwan sauce and fried rice.

info.name: Veg Fried Rice
info.description: Veg Fried Rice is a popular Asian dish that's known for its simplicity and versatility. It's made with cooked rice, stir-fried with a variety of vegetables, and seasoned with soy sauce,  sesame oil, and other aromatics.

info.name: Chicken Noodles
info.description: Chicken Noodles are a hearty and flavorful dish featuring tender chicken pieces mixed with stir-fried noodles and vegetables.

info.name: Prawns Fried Rice
info.description: Prawns Fried Rice is a flavorful and satisfying dish featuring succulent prawns stir-fried with vegetables and rice. This dish combines the sweetness of prawns with the savory taste of fried rice, making it a perfect meal for seafood lovers.

info.name: Schezwan Egg Fried Rice
info.description: Egg Schezwan Fried Rice is a vibrant, spicy, and flavorful Indo-Chinese dish made by stir-frying cooked rice with scrambled eggs, vegetables, and a tangy, spicy Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Schezwan Prawns Fried Rice
info.description: Schezwan Prawn Fried Rice is a spicy and flavorful dish that combines succulent prawns with the tangy heat of Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Mixed Fried Rice
info.description: Mixed Fried Rice is a versatile and delicious dish that combines a variety of vegetables and sometimes meats, all stir-fried with rice and seasoned with flavorful sauces. Its perfect for using up leftover rice and can be customized based on what you have on hand

info.name: Schezwan Veg Fried Rice
info.description: Schezwan Veg Fried Rice is a spicy and tangy variation of fried rice with a distinctive Schezwan flavor profile.

info.name: Paneer Fried Rice
info.description: Paneer Fried Rice is a delicious and filling dish made with cooked rice, sauteed paneer, and mixed vegetables.

info.name: Schezwan Paneer Fried Rice
info.description: Schezwan Paneer Fried Rice combines the spicy, tangy flavors of Schezwan sauce with the creamy texture of paneer and the satisfying crunch of vegetables.

info.name: Schezwan Mixed Fried Rice
info.description: Schezwan Mix Fried  Rice is a vibrant and flavorful Indo-Chinese dish that combines fragrant rice with an assortment of vegetables, all stir-fried in a spicy, tangy Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Chicken Noodles
info.description: Chicken Noodles are a hearty and flavorful dish featuring tender chicken pieces mixed with stir-fried noodles and vegetables.

info.name: Schezwan Chicken Noodles
info.description: Schezwan Chicken Noodles is a popular Indo-Chinese dish that combines spicy Schezwan sauce with tender chicken and stir-fried noodles.

info.name: Prawns Noodles
info.description: Prawn Noodles are a delicious and satisfying dish featuring tender prawns stir-fried with noodles and vegetables.

info.name: Paneer Noodles
info.description: Paneer Noodles are a delightful twist on traditional vegetable noodles, featuring cubes of paneer (Indian cottage cheese) for added protein and flavor.

info.name: Egg Noodles
info.description: Egg Noodles are a versatile and delicious type of noodle that can be used in a variety of dishes, from stir-fries to soups. They are known for their slightly chewy texture and rich flavor.

info.name: Schezwan Paneer Noodles
info.description: Schezwan Prawn Noodles are a spicy and flavorful dish featuring tender prawns and noodles tossed in a tangy Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Schezwan Egg Noodles
info.description: Schezwan Egg Noodles is a spicy and flavorful dish from Indo-Chinese cuisine, combining egg noodles with a tangy, spicy Schezwan sauce and scrambled eggs.

info.name: Schezwan Veg Noodles
info.description: Veg Schezwan Noodles is a bold, spicy, and flavorful Chinese-style stir-fry made with noodles, vegetables, and Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Veg Noodles
info.description: Veg Noodles are a vibrant and satisfying dish featuring stir-fried noodles mixed with a variety of vegetables. The noodles are cooked to a perfect texture and then tossed with finely chopped vegetables like bell peppers, carrots, and beans.

info.name: Schezwan Prawns Noodles
info.description: Schezwan Prawn Noodles are a spicy and flavorful dish featuring tender prawns and noodles tossed in a tangy Schezwan sauce.

info.name: Chicken Basmati Biryani
info.description: Basmati Chicken Biryani is a classic and aromatic Indian rice dish made with long-grain basmati rice and marinated chicken cooked together with a blend of fragrant spices.

info.name: Basmati Bucket Biryani
info.description: A grand feast of fragrant basmati rice layered with tender, spiced meat, slow-cooked to perfection and served in a generous bucket portion. Infused with traditional biryani masalas, herbs, and ghee, this biryani is perfect for family gatherings or group indulgence!

info.name: Basmati Tandoori Biryani
info.description: A royal biryani made with long-grain basmati rice layered with succulent tandoori-marinated chicken, slow-cooked with aromatic spices and herbs. Infused with smoky flavors and served with raita or salna, this biryani offers a perfect balance of heat, fragrance, and richness.

info.name: Suspense Chicken Fried Rice
info.description: Chicken Suspense Fried Rice is a bold and flavorful Indo-Chinese fusion dish with a spicy twist and a surprise element in every bite.

info.name: Suspense Chicken Noodles
info.description: Chicken Suspense Noodles is a fiery and flavorful Indo-Chinese fusion dish loaded with spicy surprises. Soft and springy noodles are tossed with marinated, fried chicken pieces, crunchy vegetables, and a bold blend of sauces like soy, chili, and garlic.

info.name: Suspense Schezwan Chicken Rice
info.description: A spicy and flavorful rice dish cooked with a special mix of Schezwan sauce and aromatic spices, tossed with tender shredded chicken, fried egg bits, and crunchy veggies. A bold Indo-Chinese creation packed with heat, texture, and taste in every bite

info.name: Suspense Schezwan Chicken Noodles
info.description: A spicy street-style noodle dish tossed with Schezwan sauce, shredded chicken, fried egg, and crunchy veggies. Loaded with bold flavors, smoky wok aroma, and a perfect balance of heat and texture a must-try for noodle lovers craving an extra punch!

info.name: Suspense Prawns Fried Rice
info.description: Prawns Suspense Fried Rice is a spicy and flavorful seafood twist on classic fried rice, packed with surprise elements in every bite.

info.name: Suspense Prawns Noodles
info.description: Prawns Suspense Noodles is a spicy and thrilling seafood noodle dish that blends Indo-Chinese flavors with bold, unexpected twists.

info.name: Indian masala tandoori
info.description: A classic tandoori dish where meat is marinated in a flavorful blend of yogurt, Indian spices, and herbs, then cooked in a traditional tandoor for a smoky, charred finish. Bursting with bold masala flavors and served sizzling hot a true taste of Indian grill mastery

info.name: Chicken Platter Shawarma
info.description: A hearty Middle Eastern-style platter loaded with juicy, spiced shawarma chicken slices, served with pita bread or kuboos, garlic mayo, fresh veggies, and a side of crispy fries or hummus. A complete and satisfying meal bursting with bold, savory flavor

info.name: Peri Peri Platter Shawarma
info.description: Peri Peri Chicken Shawarma Plated is a fiery and flavorful fusion platter that features tender chicken marinated in a bold peri peri spice blend made with red chilies, garlic, lemon juice, paprika, and herbs then grilled to smoky perfection.

info.name: Peri Peri Shawarma
info.description: Peri Peri Chicken Shawarma is a spicy, flavor-packed wrap that fuses Middle Eastern shawarma with the bold heat of African-inspired peri peri spices.

info.name: Mexican Shawarma
info.description: Mexican Shawarma is a bold fusion wrap that combines the rich spices of Middle Eastern shawarma with the zesty flair of Mexican cuisine.

info.name: Jumbo Shawarma
info.description: A super-sized, flavor-packed shawarma roll filled with layers of juicy grilled chicken, crispy veggies, creamy garlic mayo, and spicy sauces all wrapped in soft pita or kuboos. Big on taste and perfect for serious shawarma cravings

info.name: Mexican Platter Shawarma
info.description: Mexican Shawarma Plated is a flavorful fusion dish served as a deconstructed platter instead of a wrap.

info.name: Pani Poori Shawarma
info.description: Pani Puri Chicken Shawarma is a unique and playful fusion dish that combines the crunchy delight of Indian street-style pani puri with the bold flavors of Middle Eastern chicken shawarma.

info.name: Butter Chicken Gravy
info.description: Butter Chicken Gravy, also known as Murgh Makhani, is a popular North Indian dish featuring tender chicken cooked in a creamy, tomato-based gravy with a rich butter flavor. It's a beloved dish for its smooth texture and balanced taste of spices, butter, and cream

info.name: Pepper Chicken Gravy
info.description: Pepper Chicken Gravy is a flavorful South Indian dish known for its spicy kick, primarily from black pepper. This gravy combines tender chicken pieces with a robust blend of spices, including the warmth of freshly ground pepper, which gives the dish its signature heat.

info.name: Chilli Chicken Gravy
info.description: Chilli Chicken Gravy is a popular Indo-Chinese dish that combines succulent chicken pieces with a spicy, tangy, and slightly sweet gravy. This dish is characterized by its vibrant color, rich flavors, and the use of green chilies, soy sauce, and vinegar, giving it a unique taste.

info.name: Chettinad Chicken Gravy
info.description: Chicken Chettinadu Gravy is a signature dish from the Chettinad region in Tamil Nadu, known for its fiery spiciness, aromatic flavors, and the use of freshly ground spices.

info.name: Garlic Chicken Gravy
info.description: Garlic Chicken Gravy is a flavorful dish that highlights the rich aroma and taste of garlic. This dish features tender chicken cooked in a savory gravy infused with garlic, herbs, and spices.

info.name: Indian Masala Grilled
info.description: A flavorful grilled dish made with your choice of meat marinated in a rich blend of traditional Indian spices, herbs, and yogurt. Grilled to smoky perfection, it's juicy, aromatic, and packed with bold desi flavors ideal for spice lovers!

info.name: Butter Naan
info.description: Butter Naan is a soft and fluffy Indian flatbread, enriched with butter for a rich, creamy texture. It pairs beautifully with a variety of Indian curries and dishes.

info.name: Plain Naan
info.description: Plain Naan is a soft and fluffy Indian flatbread, traditionally cooked in a tandoor (clay oven), but it can also be made on a stovetop or in an oven

info.name: Plain Roti
info.description: Plain Roti is a soft, unleavened Indian flatbread made from whole wheat flour (atta) and water, cooked on a hot griddle (tava).

info.name: Butter Roti
info.description: Butter Rotti (or Butter Roti) is a variation of the traditional roti, enhanced with butter for a richer flavor and softer texture.

info.name: Blue Berry
info.description: A Blueberry Mojito is a refreshing and fruity variation of the classic mojito, with the added burst of sweet, tangy blueberries.

info.name: Watermelon
info.description: The Watermelon Mojito is a refreshing and fruity twist on the classic mojito, combining the sweet, juicy flavor of watermelon with the traditional mint, lime, and rum base.

info.name: Lime Mint
info.description: Lime Mint Mojito is a refreshing, cool beverage made with the zesty tang of fresh lime, the soothing aroma of mint leaves, and a splash of fizz.

info.name: Pineapple
info.description: Pineapple Mojito is a tropical twist on the classic mojito, blending the sweetness of fresh pineapple with the zing of lime and the cool freshness of mint.
